full_text: 1 INTERROGATORY NO. 9: Identify all persons other than Decedent who have ever committed or attempted to commit sexual misconduct or offenses against or otherwise concerning you, including, without limitation, any unwelcome behavior of a sexual nature, sexual abuse, sexual assault, threats or intimidation of a sexual nature, or sexual exploitation, regardless of whether the misconduct or offenses involved physical touching. For each person identified, identify the misconduct or offense committed, and the date and location of the misconduct or offense. 9 RESPONSE TO INTERROGATORY NO. 9: None.
